'''Willa Afahyɛ''' afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfoɔ a wɔn wɔ Takpo a ɛwɔ Nadowli mansin a ɛwɔ Atɔe Mantam mu wɔ Ghana no di<ref>https://visitghana.com/attractions/upper-west-region/</ref><ref>https://www.cwsa.gov.gh/upper-west-region-3/</ref>. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so ɛtɔ so nnan no mu<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>. Afoforo nso di no wo bosome a ɛtɔ so nnum no mu<ref>http://www.s158663955.websitehome.co.uk/ghanaculture/mod_print.php?sectionid=530</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammerɛ ntadeɛ ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi saa afahyɛ yi de da wɔn anyame no ase, wɔde srɛ akwankyerɛ ne ahobammɔ na afei nso, woyi apaya ma abosom no<ref>https://touringghana.com/upper-east-region/</ref><ref>https://ghananation.com/tourism/The-Upper-West-Region.php</ref>.

